rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0001
rows.name:
Linly, sometimes Tatsu wonder if Tatsu is too cute.
Too adorable.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0003
rows.name: As leader of BLADE team, Tatsu need cool and tough image![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0005
rows.name: Is Linly even listening to Tatsu?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0007
rows.name:
Hey, what if you got a tan?
A little color could do wonders for your image.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0008
rows.name:
In fact, I've got the perfect lotion for you.
I'll even help you apply it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0009
rows.name: Well, that... Okay, if Linly insist![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0010
rows.name: Wow, thank you, thank you, Linly![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0011
rows.name: Tanning oil smell so sweet...and...is a bit sticky...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0012
rows.name: Tanning oil? That's just plain old honey.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0013
rows.name:
It's the crucial step for a perfect chicken sauté—
the honey marinade.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0014
rows.name: Linly! Tatsu not chicken! Tatsu is Tatsu! [ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0015
rows.name: Oh, riiight. How could I forget?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs99110150_MSG0016
rows.name: Linly is not funny. Tatsu is NOT laughing.[ST:wait ]
